      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "•  Visualize a real historical commercial flight in Blender\n•  Real OpenSky flight data → aircraft animated on a textured Earth\n•  Cinematic & data-driven — not a flight simulator\n•  Deliverable: a rendered flight video",
      "originalText": "•  Visualize a real historical commercial flight in Blender\n•  Real OpenSky flight data → aircraft animated on a textured Earth\n•  Cinematic & data-driven — not a flight simulator\n•  Deliverable: a rendered flight video",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 20,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "aC"
    },
