      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782910226157,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 19,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "•  One-click add-on: OpenSky → flight.json →\n     scene\n•  Demo: Lufthansa DLH67K, Frankfurt → Madrid\n     (425 pts)\n•  16K day / 13.5K night Earth + real\n     elevation, clouds, normals\n•  Great-circle route + animated 747 + chase\n     camera\n•  UI controls: plane / altitude / terrain\n     scale + flight speed\n•  Sun synced to the flight's real UTC time",
      "originalText": "•  One-click add-on: OpenSky → flight.json →\n     scene\n•  Demo: Lufthansa DLH67K, Frankfurt → Madrid\n     (425 pts)\n•  16K day / 13.5K night Earth + real\n     elevation, clouds, normals\n•  Great-circle route + animated 747 + chase\n     camera\n•  UI controls: plane / altitude / terrain\n     scale + flight speed\n•  Sun synced to the flight's real UTC time",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 16,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "aE"
    },
