      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "•  Vertical exaggeration for the final render: true-to-scale (plane invisible from orbit)\n     vs exaggerated for visibility — now a configurable knob (currently plane ×100, altitude\n     ×10)\n•  Weather source: ERA5 (rich, heavy) vs Open-Meteo (simple JSON) → leaning ERA5\n•  Weather look: 2D texture on cloud shell vs volumetric vs sky shader → leaning texture\n     shell",
      "originalText": "•  Vertical exaggeration for the final render: true-to-scale (plane invisible from orbit)\n     vs exaggerated for visibility — now a configurable knob (currently plane ×100, altitude\n     ×10)\n•  Weather source: ERA5 (rich, heavy) vs Open-Meteo (simple JSON) → leaning ERA5\n•  Weather look: 2D texture on cloud shell vs volumetric vs sky shader → leaning texture\n     shell",
